.DT 
give_money 
Discworld monster help 
give_money 

Name
.SI 5
give_money - Setup default money.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int give_money(int base, int rand, string type);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Gives the monster base+random(rand) coins of the type 'type'.  This
is the general method of giveing a monster its default amount of money.
This function returns the total amount of money the monster now has
in the coinage specified.  If no coin type is given then the default
type is copper.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
money
.EP
